  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Protester arrested on plane",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "One of the Khali mask protesters who was ready to travel to Dubai by plane was arrested by the CIT earlier.",
        "A civil activist named Danis Ali was thus arrested inside the plane that was going to travel to Dubai. \"If there is a travel ban against me, he could have arrested himself at the airport before boarding the flight... If there are documents for arrest, the authorities should show them.\" It can also be seen that Danis Ali is demanding from the authorities when he is arrested.",
        "A video of unresponsive officers arresting and dragging Danis Ali, who was sitting on a seat inside the plane, is currently going viral on social media."
      ],
